        "text_MD8WVp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Mountains have always held meaning. They stand for strength, for patience, and for the quiet courage it takes to rise.  At BearWell, they represent more than a destination. They are the shape of the journey itself - of mind, body, and spirit moving through challenge and change. </p><p>The mountains on our packaging reflect this rhythm. Peaks mark the moments we pause - to honour what we’ve built, to breathe in what we’ve become. They’re not endpoints, but perspectives - places of clarity before the next ascent.  </p><p>And the valleys? They’re where growth deepens - where we leave behind the comfort of the known, and build resilience, one quiet step at a time.  Together, these rises and falls remind us: the journey doesn’t end. It carries on - shaping us, step by step, into who we’re meant to become.</p>",
